OL,3,CHomes evacuated after Scarborough
OL,4,Chouse explosion
OL,6,FDozens of properties have been
OL,7,Fevacuated and residents have been
OL,8,Fasked to avoid part of Scarborough
OL,9,Fafter an explosion partially destroyed
OL,10,Fa house.
OL,12,FNorth Yorkshire Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService was called to Cambridge Street
OL,14,Fat about 5.45am on Friday, 8 May.
OL,16,FPictures from the scene showed the
OL,17,Frear wall of the terraced property had
OL,18,Fcollapsed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
