OL,3,CHomes evacuated after Scarborough
OL,4,Chouse explosion
OL,6,FFirefighters are working alongside the
OL,7,Fambulance service, police and the gas
OL,8,Fboard at the scene.
OL,10,FUp to 50 homes have been evacuated and
OL,11,Fthe public is being asked to avoid the
OL,12,Farea while emergency services from
OL,13,FScarborough, Sherburn, Robin Hoods Bay
OL,14,Fdeal with the incident.
OL,16,FCrews are using breathing apparatus to
OL,17,Fextinguish the fire.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
