OL,3,CHomes evacuated after Scarborough
OL,4,Chouse explosion
OL,6,FA North Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our officers attended the
OL,8,Flocation immediately, working
OL,9,Falongside North Yorkshire Fire and
OL,10,FRescue Service to evacuate local
OL,11,Fresidents, and close roads in the
OL,12,Farea, to keep people safe.
OL,14,F"Emergency services remain at the
OL,15,Fscene, and we ask members of the
OL,16,Fpublic to avoid the area at this time."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
